# Git Commit Format

Always use git commit -s to sign off on the commit
Format: `<type>(scope): <description>`

Types:
- `feat` - New feature
- `fix` - Bug fix
- `docs` - Documentation
- `style` - Formatting
- `refactor` - Code changes
- `test` - Tests
- `chore` - Maintenance